Class ExtractVisitData

  • java.lang.Object
    • datasource.ExtractVisitData

  • public class ExtractVisitData
extends java.lang.Object
    The ExtractVisitData class is used to extract data from the file saved from the membership system into a temporary file called 'temp_extracted.txt'. Note: the file could have also been a csv.
    Author:
    LoganDuck

      • removeEmptyIndices

        public static java.lang.String[] removeEmptyIndices(java.lang.String[] arr)
        removeEmptyIndices will take an array and remove indices that are empty or contain null values.

        For example:
        If we have,
        {"This", "", "", "is", "an", " ", "example"}

        This method will return,
        {"This", "is", "an", "example"}
